[CD單曲|CD單曲]]。<ref name="cdsingle">{{cite web|url=http://www.amazon.com/LIMITED-Begin-Again-Single-CD/dp/B009YJ93X8/|title=LIMITED EDITION 'Begin Again' Single CD|publisher=[[Amazon.com|Amazon.com]] (US) Amazon, Inc|accessdate=2012-12-13|archive-date=2016-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160208230425/http://www.amazon.com/LIMITED-Begin-Again-Single-CD/dp/B009YJ93X8/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="cdsingle1">{{cite web|url=http://store.taylorswift.com/LIMITED-EDITION-Begin-Again-Single/dp/B009YJ93X8?field_availability=-2&field_browse=3228049011&field_product_site_launch_date_utc=-1y&id=LIMITED+EDITION+Begin+Again+Single&ie=UTF8&refinementHistory=brandtextbin%2Csubjectbin%2Ccolor_map%2Cprice%2Csize_name&searchNodeID=3228049011&searchPage=1&searchRank=salesrank&searchSize=12|title=LIMITED EDITION 'Begin Again' Single CD|work={{noitalics|store.taylorswift.com}}|publisher=[[Amazon.com|Amazon.com]] (US) Amazon, Inc|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6D2DjuwAg?url=http://store.taylorswift.com/LIMITED-EDITION-Begin-Again-Single/dp/B009YJ93X8|archivedate=2012-12-19|accessdate=2012-12-19|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

==商業表現==
歌曲數位發行當天在幾小時之內即迅速登上iTunes美國下載榜首位，是第一首將《[[江南Style|江南Style]]》趕下下載即時熱度冠軍的歌曲。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a409276/psy-gangnam-style-tops-aussie-singles-chart.html |title=Psy 'Gangnam Style' tops Aussie singles chart |work=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]] |first=Robert |last=Copsey |date=2012-10-01 |accessdate=2013-04-28 |archive-date=2012-12-13 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6CtJCqdDA?url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a409276/psy-gangnam-style-tops-aussie-singles-chart.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2012年9月30日，歌曲以299,000份數位銷量獲得了[[告示牌熱門數位單曲榜|《告示牌》熱門數位單曲榜]]冠軍，成為泰勒絲在該榜單第五首冠軍歌曲。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/474813/mumford-sons-green-day-no-doubt-debut-at-nos-1-3-on-billboard-200-chart |title=Mumford & Sons, Green Day, No Doubt Debut at Nos. 1-3 on Billboard 200 Chart |work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] |date=2012-10-03 |accessdate=2012-10-03 |archive-date=2013-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130719181958/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/474813/mumford-sons-green-day-no-doubt-debut-at-nos-1-3-on-billboard-200-chart |dead-url=no }}</ref> 憑藉歌曲首週的高銷量，2012年10月4日，歌曲空降[[告示牌百强单曲榜|告示牌百强单曲榜]]第7名。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/474810/psy-cant-beat-maroon-5-in-close-race-for-hot-100s-top-spot |title=PSY Can't Beat Maroon 5 In Close Race For Hot 100's Top Spot |work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] |date=2012-10-03 |accessdate=2012-10-03 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304105124/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/474810/psy-cant-beat-maroon-5-in-close-race-for-hot-100s-top-spot |dead-url=no }}</ref> 歌曲總共在榜20週，被[[美國唱片業協會|美國唱片業協會]]認證為白金唱片。

全球範圍內，歌曲也獲得了一定的商業成功。在加拿大，《重新開始》空降[[加拿大百強單曲榜|加拿大百強單曲榜]]第4名，是泰勒絲第6首進入該榜單前5的歌曲。在澳大利亞，歌曲於2012年9月30日空降榜單第20名。<ref>{{cite web|last=Copsey|first=Robert|title=Psy 'Gangnam Style' tops Aussie singles chart|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a409276/psy-gangnam-style-tops-aussie-singles-chart.html|work=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]|publisher=[[Nat_Mags|Nat Mags]]|accessdate=2012-10-01|date=2012-10-01|archive-date=2012-12-13|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6CtJCqdDA?url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a409276/psy-gangnam-style-tops-aussie-singles-chart.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在英國，歌曲空降[[英國單曲榜|英國單曲榜]]第30名，是《紅色》中第二支進入前40名的單曲。在紐西蘭、愛爾蘭和西班牙，歌曲的最高排位分別是11、25和30。

